    "Twitter is indeed a resource-rich platform for sentiment analysis, but it is not the only platform where financial discussions take place.",
    "Hence, our future work could focus on a more rounded approach that could involve examining other social media platforms, such as Reddit and Facebook.",
    "Furthermore, mainstream news sources including YouTube broadcasts and traditional television news channels might offer a fuller, multi-dimensional view of market sentiment that is not currently accounted for in our model.",
    "This consideration would allow us to capture people's opinions with far more accuracy than potentially leading an accurate predictions.",
